DECLARE


/*++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Finalidade:   Obter o CID da conta
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
